---
title: Carb Smart Barramundi and Lemony Lentil Bowl with Garlicky Feta Crema
description: Golden seared barramundi fillets get a flavour boost from a garlicky feta cheese sauce and sit atop a bed of lemony lentils, roasted sweet potatoes and ever-so-slightly wilted baby spinach. Eat until your heart's content with this carb-conscious bowl.

